Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.12,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:122080,126126}With Masumi's help, Maya gets a substitute\Nrole in "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:11.59,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126126,131590}However, the co-stars who thought\Nof Maya as a "stage storm…"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:15.05,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:131590,135052}…try to trap her by replacing\Nthe new revised script with the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:20.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:135052,140097}Maya gets on the stage without knowing\Nher words or the storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.10,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147105}{\an5\pos(766,710)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,0)}—Episode 17—\NWhere is Mr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:42.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157824,162287}Just watch.\NI will make this play flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162287,166333}This scene is where Chie is overwhelmed\Nby her mortifying feelings…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166333,169044}…and shouts that she would rather run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169044,172923}But Maya doesn't know that,\Nor even her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172923,175926}Himekawa Ayumi doesn't know\Nher words, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175926,178303}She ran out onto the stage\Nwhen it wasn't even her turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178303,183392}Let's see what they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192359,196863}With that lily in your mouth, are you going\Nto entertain me just like your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199032,203704}I just heard that your father\Nhas become a traveling entertainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203704,206998}What a shame\Nto the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207624,211211}What should I do?\NI can't keep quiet forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211211,212838}Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212838,216508}I want to hear your opinion\Nas Kaidōji Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216508,218635}As Kaidōji Chie…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218635,221972}Just answer my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221972,224558}I will answer\Nto your words as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:49.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225767,229646}Ayumi is telling me to proceed\Nwith this scene with all ad-lib.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230939,233316}Do you understand, Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233316,235736}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235736,237946}She accepted the challenge.\NWhat a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237946,240574}I'll just follow Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240574,245620}I wonder, do you remember\Nwhen you first came to this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:10.45,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:246663,250459}Ayumi told Maya Chie's situation\Nin her own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:15.83,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:250459,255839}Chie was born to Yukihiro, the fifth son\Nof Kaidōji, and a geisha from Fukagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:21.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:255839,261970}Yukihiro has returned with Chie once,\Nbut he left her to be with another geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261970,266308}Everyone used to mistake you as a maid,\Nbecause you were always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:32.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268018,272981}Ayumi, do you want\Nto make me sad or mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274149,277068}What do you think about this flier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279946,284242}What a great father, to have his\Npicture on something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284242,287245}I see, she's trying\Nto make me upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287245,289498}What a great father he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291041,291958}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293084,294669}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294669,296713}That's it.\NNow we're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297547,300258}What nonsense!\NAre you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300258,303553}He dishonored the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303553,305597}What about the Kaidōji family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305597,309309}All they did was to try and make\Nmy loving father and mother separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309309,310477}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310477,314731}What an ungrateful thing to say\Nafter all they have done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314731,319945}No! The Kaidōji family, who influences things\Nwith its power and money, I hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324324,326284}Such brave actresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326284,329371}They match each other's emotions and words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329371,332165}Besides, they are almost\Nfollowing the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332165,335752}All they have to do now is to get Chie\Nto run off the stage saying she would run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336461,340173}Is that right?\NThen, why don't you run away, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341049,344260}You and your father are a stain on our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344260,347097}Everyone has to live unpleasantly\Nbecause of that stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347097,349516}Why don't you go\Nto that geisha mother of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349516,352060}Or go after your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360068,362529}He's a poor actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362529,365407}Why don't you go with the poor actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365407,367367}I hate this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370120,372956}I want to say that I want to leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372956,375041}But what if that's not in the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375041,376001}I'll make a terrible mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396313,399149}This… This house…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399149,401860}I'll… I'll go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401860,403445}She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403445,405864}I never want to see your face again, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405864,407407}Go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407407,408700}Get off the stage from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418710,421003}Excellent job.\NYou did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421003,424925}Uh, my last words,\Nwas that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424925,429763}Okay? Without these words,\Nthe play couldn't have gone on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429763,431097}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431097,436269}Chie's running away triggers\Nthe breakdown of the Kaidōji family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436269,438813}It was that important…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438813,442984}I might not have said those words\Nif Ayumi didn't hit me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442984,446780}What, Chie is leaving the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447864,450241}Ayumi, what a talented person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464214,466549}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466549,467968}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467968,471888}We wouldn't have known\Nwhat to do if you didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471888,476017}Then you should learn from this and never\Ndo a stupid thing like switching a script again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478979,480146}She knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484401,486861}Ayumi, thank you so—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486861,488029}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.40,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:490114,491408}Backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:18.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493493,498748}Ayumi, she completely brought me into\Nher pace and made me say the needed words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498748,501376}I can't win.\NI can't beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:30.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503920,510260}Kitajima Maya. She used her full body to sense\Nwhere I as going, and followed me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510260,512679}She was as good as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:38.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512679,518643}No, I knew the storyline of the fourth act,\Nso I had the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518643,521020}She still did as good as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524357,526651}I lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530196,533450}Ayumi, a person\Nwith such a great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533450,534993}Mr. Himekawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536870,539539}Director!\NAyumi did great on stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:07.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543668,547464}Her father is a movie director\Nand her mother a well-known actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:11.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547464,551134}She has a shining beauty\Nand a genius of a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551134,555472}Compared to her,\Nhow boring am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555472,557307}What's wrong, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557307,560602}You seem down despite\Nyour great success tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560602,563103}Ayumi saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563103,566858}It wasn't my work,\Nbut Ayumi's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566858,569861}Let me take you home.\NIt's pouring outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569861,572822}No, thank you!\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572822,575533}You still hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575533,577202}Yes, I hate you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577202,581039}Aren't you glad that things\Nare going your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581039,587504}You should be satisfied when you have\Nthe play rights for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589631,591299}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592759,596387}I get what I want\Nusing any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596387,598431}I don't give a damn\Nwhat happens to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600517,602852}Are you happy to hear me\Nsay that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604062,605396}How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:10.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606064,610527}Such a terrible person.\NAs cold-blooded as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616032,618409}I won't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618409,619953}I will never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626835,630296}I wonder if Maya is looking\Nfor her mom in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633466,635218}Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635218,637637}You're soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637637,639806}I can't become "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642058,643059}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643059,647564}Even if I run as hard as I can,\NI can never catch up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653236,657574}Mr. Masumi, what have you been\Nthinking about all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657574,659284}Could I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659284,660368}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660368,663371}The girl who ran from you,\NKitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665957,667458}I must be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667458,672046}She was wonderful today,\Ndespite what all happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672046,677177}You almost lost yourself then,\Nunlike your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677177,680930}I was just worried that\Nshe would ruin the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680930,682056}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682056,685059}What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685059,687270}I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688938,691357}Yes, that was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691357,693484}That was all…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696487,699282}I feel drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700116,702285}I can't find my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702285,705246}I can't even practice acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:52.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706581,712670}Sakurakōji didn't come\Nto "The Smile of Stone" at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:57.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712670,717717}How lonely.\NEveryone's gone all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717967,720511}Maya, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721262,724474}It's him!\NLook at the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724474,725892}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725892,730897}It's like a sugar daddy\Nwith all this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731272,733900}"I saw your act\Nin {\i0}The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals{\i1}."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733900,738154}"I was impressed with your act as Chie,\Neven as a substitute."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738154,740198}"I'm looking forward to seeing you\Non stage again soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741741,745161}You were there again for me,\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:33.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748039,753711}I still have someone on my side.\NMr. Purple Rose.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:33.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:753711,753711}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:37.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:757507,757507}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:40.46,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:760468,760468}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.47,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:761803,765473}Maya enrolled in Hitotsubashi High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:51.77,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:765473,771771}It's known as the "talent school," and there are\Nmany actors and actresses in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:58.82,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:771771,778820}{\fs70}Then there's an elite acting club, members of which\Nare known to have passed challenging acting tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:04.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779696,784701}I wonder what they are like, winning\Nthe "All-Japan Acting Contest" every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784701,785868}{\an8}The demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785868,786911}{\an8}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786911,789539}{\an8}Hide the babies,\Nhide the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787620,789539}Look, that's Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789539,792333}The best actress of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792333,793626}Kanaya Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797839,801968}The demon!\NIt's here, the baby eater is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803720,806597}Where are the children!?\NWhere are the kids!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806597,809100}If not them,\NI'll eat you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809100,810893}Go away, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:40.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816357,820278}"The scene, played as an ad-lib\Nby Kitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi…"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820278,822530}"…was an unexpected plus\Nfor the night's play."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:43.69,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:818735,823698}The Cherry Tree\Nof Dream Festivals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:46.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822530,826117}"Much is expected from their\Ncompetitive yet equal talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831289,834334}"Their competitive yet equal talent…"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842759,843926}What talent…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844677,847221}Are you Ms. Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847221,849349}Uhm, yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849349,853436}This was left at the reception desk\Nwith your name and class on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854354,855605}Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857357,858358}Oh, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858358,859817}Sorry, I'll get it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860401,862236}Please wait for me.\NDon't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865031,866616}Where is he?\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867575,868826}What a nice car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878169,880880}A purple rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880880,882507}Whose car is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882507,885176}Hayami Masumi.\NFrom Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885176,886677}Hayami Masumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886677,888638}He just went into\Nthe Principal's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888638,891516}He's a great businessman.\NI hear he donates lots of money every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891516,895353}Yeah, thinking that students\Nwill bring him money in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895353,897855}A purple rose in the car\Nof Metropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:02.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897855,902901}Perhaps Mr. Purple Rose\Nwas in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905988,909700}And he might be in the\NPrincipal's office with Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:12.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911744,912954}He must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915706,916833}H-Hey, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916833,918668}Sorry, but I need to see the Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918668,920294}He has a guest right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924674,926092}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926092,930138}Yes. I'm Kitajima Maya\Nfrom Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930138,931806}Well, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931806,935184}Hell, little girl.\NDid you come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935184,939564}No! I'm looking for\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939564,941858}Hmph.\NMr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941858,945570}I saw a purple rose in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945570,948030}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948030,951200}You know him.\NYou know Mr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951200,953619}Please tell me who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953619,962128}All I want to do is tell him how much\NI appreciate him… for all he does for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962128,963671}How much he encourages me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965923,967800}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967800,972555}Oh, I just remembered who had the purple rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972555,976809}I picked up an actress on the way here,\Nand she had some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976809,978102}An actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979479,983107}She had some flowers with purple roses in it,\Nso she must be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983107,986819}Sorry it's not who\Nyou were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986819,988988}I thought I could finally thank him…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989906,992909}He knows how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998873,1001250}Please shut the door\Nwhen you are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002043,1004253}Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:59.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015097,1019977}"May your school life be filled\Nwith joy and achievement."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021270,1024774}I want to see you,\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024774,1026442}I wonder what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026442,1029278}I want to see him, and thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032281,1035242}Hey, welcome home.\NHow was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035242,1038120}Look at this!\NIt's Mr. Purple Rose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038120,1041123}He came to your school?\NWhew, what a love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041123,1043584}Stop it, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045545,1048839}I wonder when I can go\Non stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048839,1052176}I want Mr. Purple Rose\Nto see me on stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052176,1058057}Teacher didn't order you off the stage out of hate,\Nand she'll get you back on there again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058057,1059684}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059684,1063479}Why don't you come and see our practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065481,1067692}Are you Ms. Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067692,1068734}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068734,1071028}This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071028,1073698}Hasegawa,\NMetropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073698,1075658}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079579,1081330}The role of Helen Keller?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081330,1086002}Yes. Well, we have a total\Nof five candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086002,1090089}We'll have an audition in August\Nto make our final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090089,1091757}Audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091757,1097138}Helen Keller has a triple disability\Nand acts like a wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097138,1098514}It will be a tough role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098514,1101809}Who are the other candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101809,1104061}Shiratori Reina,\NHayakawa Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104061,1106063}She's an upcoming actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106063,1107481}Kanaya Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107481,1109817}Kanaya Emi?\NFrom Hitotsubashi High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111986,1114572}Yes.\NShe's full of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114572,1116407}So, who is the fourth one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116407,1117867}Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117867,1120077}Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120077,1124957}Let me also mention that\Nthe director will be Onedera Hajime…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124957,1128961}…and the main role, Annie Sullivan,\Nwill be played by Himekawa Utako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128961,1132006}Ha!\NThat's a fair competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132006,1133966}It's like Maya going\Ninto enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136052,1137803}Please don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137803,1140723}Our audition is very fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140723,1145853}The fact that Himekawa Ayumi is the daughter\Nof the main role won't affect it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145853,1149398}Then I guess that's okay.\NHuh, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149398,1152276}Thank you for the offer,\Nbut I would like to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152276,1153277}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153277,1156238}I would like to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156238,1158866}Maya, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158866,1161202}This role sure is hard,\Nbut it's a rewarding challenge, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161202,1164163}You will grow as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164163,1168209}I know you're not thrilled about Metropolitan\NEntertainment, but think of the bigger picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168209,1170503}You have to grab your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170503,1173631}Well, please take your time\Nto think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173631,1176092}I won't take the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176092,1178719}Please change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182390,1184475}What's wrong?\NIt's not like you, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184475,1187603}I can't win.\NI can't win against Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187603,1189105}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200241,1202993}You really are going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202993,1204203}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204203,1204954}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204954,1206539}I will be at the mansion in Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206539,1211210}Practice hard.\NI'll talk to your grandmother every three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211210,1215089}The next time I see you,\Nit will be at the audition, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215089,1219218}Yes. Until then, we won't be\Nmother and daughter anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219218,1222638}Yes. I want to get the role with my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222638,1227226}I will choose Helen fairly\Nfrom an actress' point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228477,1231105}Good bye now, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231105,1232982}Good bye, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239029,1241991}I heard you declined\Nthe audition for Helen's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241991,1243242}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243242,1244869}You are afraid of Ayumi,\Nis that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244869,1246454}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246454,1250124}You got scared after being lead by Ayumi\Nin "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252418,1255045}Maya, you are hereby expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255045,1256255}Expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256255,1259967}You knew you weren't allowed\Nto get on stage, yet you took that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259967,1262386}That's reason enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263137,1264346}Expelled…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265556,1270019}But, if you win the role of Helen,\Nthen I'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270019,1271228}Helen's role?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271228,1275816}If not, you can not only forget about practicing\Nat my school, but "The Crimson Goddess" as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:20.27,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1277818,1280279}Metropolitan Entertainment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283783,1285201}You're still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286243,1289955}It's my way of taking a break\Nto read the proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289955,1293167}Sounds like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293167,1296754}About "The Miracle Worker,"\Nwe'll have the interview next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296754,1299590}The audition is for August 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299590,1301091}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301926,1306263}I see that you haven't heard if\NKitajima Maya will be at the audition or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306263,1307515}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307515,1310392}Don't worry. She replied\Nand she will be at the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314063,1317566}Maybe you should send\Nsome purple roses to encourage her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.61,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326116,1328619}Maya, you are hereby expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:15.62,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330996,1335626}But, if you win the role of Helen,\Nthen I'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339630,1342007}I will play the disabled Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342007,1344176}Acting is all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:30.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348722,1350641}Go for it, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:36.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350641,1356063}If you can play Helen, then you will be\None step closer to "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:47.65,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1359358,1367658}To continue with acting as her future, she has\Nto win the role of Helen Keller, Maya told herself.
Comment: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:49.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1369368,1369368}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:02.71,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1376585,1382715}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:08.80,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1382715,1388805}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:20.81,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1388805,1400815}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
