Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:38.83,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1412955,1418835}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:44.96,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1418835,1424965}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:51.05,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1424965,1431055}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:57.14,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1431055,1437145}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
